{"tid":1879532,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"因應日本疫情升溫 台灣對日本發出一級旅遊警示","createTime":"2020-02-14T08:56:34.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-14T08:58:45.000Z","uid":60545,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"03cdce91b3212880888d6af7c65b59ac402dd8f3","tid":1879532,"uid":60545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-14T08:56:34.000Z","msg":"日本國內武漢肺炎疫情升溫，台灣中央流行疫情指揮中心今天宣布，即日起提升日本的旅遊疫情建議到第一級注意（Watch），民眾應遵守當地的一般預防措施。<br />\n<br />\n除台灣之外，國際間累計565例確診病例，分布於26個國家/地區；病例數以國際運輸工具（日本鑽石公主號）218例、新加坡58例、香港53例、泰國33例及日本30例為多；病例中3例死亡，分別為日本、香港及菲律賓各1例。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/life/breakingnews/3068196\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Flife%2Fbreakingnews%2F3068196&d=NEgIrN0XKBZxjsPVzjJKR9g1hcd%2FKl8HgBLPnoE2n08%3D&h=2ad0c1c1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Flife%2Fbreakingnews%2F3068196&h=346c525f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/life/breakingnews/3068196</a>"},{"pid":"a6b069a8b347b24b9a5e86187c2fa03208c2734b","tid":1879532,"uid":80724,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-14T08:58:45.000Z","msg":"爭氣啦日本<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}